sys_remote_update_set.description:
@Author: Frank Schuster
@Release Date: 2016-12-21
@Version: 2.0

## Service Portal - Report Widget ##
This update set contains the following elements:
- ngTable as a UI Script (CDN provides a 404 - see reported issue in the Github repo) & ngTable stylesheet (CSS) 
- Chart.js (2.4.0) & Angular Chart JS (1.0.3) with JS & CSS Includes. Chart.js ships with Service Portal, but in an older version, that e.g. does not allow Stacked Bar Reports
- Widget Dependencies for ng-Table & chart.js (ATTENTION: the OOTB Dependency for chart.js has been renamed to chart.js-old! Apply the "Chart.js Fix" Update set before applying this update set to make sure this change is made before the commit, otherwise you will run into a duplicate error for the angular module)
- "ChartJS Report" widget that allows rendering of backend reports within Service Portal
- New Table "Service Portal Report Instances" extends Instance [sp_instance] to hold all custom options for the Report widget
